{"tid":1304741,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"再去整連儂牆嘅唔該入一入黎","createTime":"2019-07-10T16:39:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-11T05:49:04.000Z","uid":265197,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ce9cab4861c38f3fc0443f0a136ac9fa0c67527b","tid":1304741,"uid":265197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T16:39:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">麻煩整多塊係寫我地5大訴求，<br />\n同埋帶少少類似呢d圖<br />\n係差佬建制派政府做嘅衰野<br />\n唔使長編大論全部寫齊唔使人人一樣<br />\n次次被清完再帶唔同仲好<br />\n但最緊要有野睇<br />\n同埋老坑中坑眼唔好<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">字</span><span style=\"color: green;\">體</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">一</span><span style=\"color: purple;\">定</span><span style=\"color: violet;\">要</span><span style=\"color: brown;\">大</span><span style=\"color: pink;\">隻</span></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jJhOoh2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjJhOoh2.jpg&h=e7d7c979&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">等街坊耳濡目染</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">日日見到黑警暴行</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好齋整塊紙皮仔<br />\n人地撐警都識大大隻字寫佢做乜鬼野<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">咩柒資訊都無仲要豆潤咁細張紙</span><br />\n屋企樓下夠有通告喇你會唔會埋去逐張睇?<br />\n人地寫膠野人地嘅事<br />\n如果齋整留言版嘅不如咪鬼搞<br />\n而家抗爭唔係兒戲麻煩玩得黎都認真d<br />\n咁hea你對唔對得住被捕等緊上庭要坐監嘅同路人</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人加油</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9e0f389b888ebdecafc606f95bb5d8b1a5b796d","tid":1304741,"uid":49781,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T16:41:34.000Z","msg":"我有寫嘅，不過唔夠大隻係真<br />\n<br />\n個人認為太多「失敗論」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1304668\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1304668</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},